slike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7ffba7333afe900a60c032ce685754a79373edbe","tid":2226572,"uid":158270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:29:11.000Z","msg":"去憎個符號而唔係個權力本身，已經係絕望嘅體現。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:44:17.000Z","msg":"見到都得啖笑，<br />\n藍色本身完全就冇問題，甚至我覺得佢係其中一隻顏色代表到香港<br />\n<br />\n由古南越遺民嘅海洋文明/生產，到近代嘅英軍開埠、接受西方文明、發展做轉口港...<br />\n<br />\n香港發展同歷史根本離唔開海洋<br />\n<br />\n最代表到海洋亦好自然係藍色/波浪紋（國旗嘅話，例如Zeeland果枝咁）<br />\n<br />\n當然我完全體會到香港人有幾討厭以藍色做主調嘅警察<br />\n但唔代表藍色就係原罪<br />\n<br />\n唔通德國佬會因為nazi就唔用黑色同紅色做佢哋國旗其中一個顏色？當然唔會啦，已碼唔會一開始就ban死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21deb60816fdbf5068b821d43497fe9aa3d8b02a","tid":2226572,"uid":35737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦 天琦件衫都係藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ecff74bf7b66243dd6341f381b9fb86afa6445","tid":2226572,"uid":182935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb0e1e6d0e20a502f0f3c932f3ea550765c06ac","tid":2226572,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"本民藍"}]}